rtner\"><a href=\"../partner/\" class=\"st-Header_Nav_Link\">取扱施設</a></li>\n          <li class=\"st-Header_Nav_Item st-Header_Nav_Item-howtouse\"><a href=\"../howtouse/\" class=\"st-Header_Nav_Link\">レンズの取扱い方法</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <ul class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other\">\n          <li class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Item st-Header_Nav_Other_Item-feature\"><a href=\"../feature/\" class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Link\">私たち<span class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Sm\">の</span>特長</a></li>\n          <li class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Item st-Header_Nav_Other_Item-company\"><a href=\"../company/\" class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Link\">会社情報</a></li>\n          <li class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Item\"><a href=\"https://www.sun-con.com/medical-comfirm/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"st-Header_Nav_Other_Link\">眼科医療機器</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n      <div class=\"st-Header_En\"><a href=\"https://www.sun-con.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"st-Header_En_Link\"><img src=\"../common/img/btn_en_01.svg\" width=\"55\" height=\"30\" alt=\"ENG\" class=\"st-Header_En_Image\"></a></div>\n      <div class=\"st-Header_otoiawase\"> <a href=\"https://www.sun-con.com/contact/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"st-Header_otoiawase_Link\"><img src=\"../common/img/btn_otoiawase_01.svg\" width=\"75\" height=\"30\" alt=\"ENG\" class=\"st-Header_otoiawase_Image\"> </a> </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"st-Header_Trigger\"><span class=\"st-Header_Trigger_Inner\"></span></div>\n</header>\n<!-- / .st-Header -->\n\n<article class=\"st-Content\">\n  <h1 class=\"st-PageTitle\"><span class=\"st-PageTitle_Inner\">コンタクトレンズ</span></h1>\n  <ul class=\"st-BreadCrumbs\">\n    <li class=\"st-BreadCrumbs_Item\"><a href=\"../\" class=\"st-BreadCrumbs_Link\">カスタムメイドレンズ［株式会社 サンコンタクトレンズ］トップページ</a></li>\n    <li class=\"st-BreadCrumbs_Item\">コンタクトレンズ</li>\n  </ul>\n  <section class=\"contactlensfr-Intro\">\n    <div class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Inner\">\n      <h2 class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Title\">カスタムメイドレンズ<span class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Title_Sm\">とは</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Text\">素材とレンズタイプ、ベベルデザインの指定、追加加工の組み合わせにより無限の選択肢が生まれます。</p>\n      <div class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Btn\"><a href=\"feature.html\" class=\"sw-Btn03\">詳細はこちら</a></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Image\"><img src=\"img/img_contactlensfr_01.png\" width=\"670\" height=\"184\" alt=\"材質×レンズタイプ×ベベルデザイン×追加加工=カスタムメイド\" class=\"contactlensfr-Intro_Image_Item sw-ImageText\"></div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content\">\n    <section class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Item contactlensfr-Content_Item-material\">\n      <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Inner\">\n        <h2 class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Title\"><img src=\"img/h2_contactlensfr_01.png\" width=\"544\" height=\"164\" alt=\"材質\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Title_Image\"></h2>\n        <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Text\">酸素透過性のバランスが良く、UVカット、水濡れ性などの特性を持った、<span class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Text_Lg\">丈夫で取り扱いやすい材質</span>を揃えています。</p>\n        <ul class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu js-inview sw-fadeinview\">\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item-milduv\"><a href=\"milduv.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image\"><img src=\"img/btn_contactlensfr_01.png\" width=\"270\" height=\"220\" alt=\"サンコンマイルドUV\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image_Item\"></div>\n            </a></li>\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item-mildi\"><a href=\"mildi.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image\"><img src=\"img/btn_contactlensfr_02.png\" width=\"270\" height=\"220\" alt=\"サンコンマイルドi\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image_Item\"></div>\n            </a></li>\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item-mildepi\"><a href=\"mildepi.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image\"><img src=\"img/btn_contactlensfr_03.png\" width=\"270\" height=\"220\" alt=\"サンコンマイルドEpi\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image_Item\"></div>\n            </a></li>\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Item-mild2\"><a href=\"mild2.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image\"><img src=\"img/btn_contactlensfr_04.png\" width=\"270\" height=\"220\" alt=\"サンコンマイルドⅡ\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Menu_Image_Item\"></div>\n            </a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Item contactlensfr-Content_Item-lenstype\">\n      <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Inner js-inview sw-fadeinview\">\n        <h2 class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Title\"><img src=\"img/h2_contactlensfr_02.png\" width=\"544\" height=\"164\" alt=\"材質\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Title_Image\"></h2>\n        <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Text\">見え方と症状に応じたさまざまなレンズタイプがあります。</p>\n        <ul class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case\">\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Item\"><a href=\"kinshienshi.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Image\"><img src=\"img/img_contactlensfr_02.png\" width=\"670\" height=\"335\" alt=\"\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Image_Item\"></div>\n            <h3 class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Title\">近視・遠視</h3>\n            <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Text\">遠くや近くが見えづらい、痛み・乾燥・充血などがある。</p>\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Btn\"><span class=\"sw-Btn03\">近視・遠視が気になる<br>\n              あなたはこちら</span></div>\n            </a></li>\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Item\"><a href=\"ranshi.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Image\"><img src=\"img/img_contactlensfr_03.png\" width=\"670\" height=\"335\" alt=\"\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Image_Item\"></div>\n            <h3 class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Title\">乱視・不正乱視</h3>\n            <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Text\">ぼやけて見える、レンズがはずれやすいなどの症状がある。</p>\n            <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Btn\"><span class=\"sw-Btn03\">乱視・不正乱視が気になる<br>\n              あなたはこちら</span></p>\n            </a></li>\n          <li class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Item\"><a href=\"enkin.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Link\">\n            <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Image\"><img src=\"img/img_contactlensfr_04.png\" width=\"670\" height=\"335\" alt=\"\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Image_Item\"></div>\n            <h3 class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Title\">遠近両用</h3>\n            <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Text\">小さい文字が見えにくい、ピントが合いづらいと感じている。</p>\n            <p class=\"contactlensfr-Content_Case_Btn\"><span class=\"sw-Btn03\">遠近両用をお考えの<br>\n              あなたはこちら</span></p>\n            </a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase js-inview sw-fadeinview\">\n          <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Btn contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Btn-ranshi\"> <a href=\"kyodoranshi.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Link\"> <img src=\"img/btn_contactlensfr_05.svg\" width=\"141\" height=\"42\" alt=\"強度の不正乱視でお困りの方へ\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Btn_Image\"></a></div>\n          <div class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Btn contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Btn-hakunaisyou\"> <a href=\"cataract.html\" style=\"pointer-events: auto\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Link\"> <img src=\"img/btn_contactlensfr_06.svg\" width=\"189\" height=\"42\" alt=\" お子さんが先天白内障と言われたら\" class=\"contactlensfr-Content_OtherCase_Btn_Image\"></a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n  <ul class=\"contactlensfr-Info js-inview sw-fadeinview\">\n    <li class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Item\"><a href=\"buy.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Link\">\n      <h2 class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Title\">レンズの購入方法</h2>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Text\">一般的な購入方法についてご案内しています。</p>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Btn\"><span class=\"sw-Btn03\">詳細はこちら</span></p>\n      </a></li>\n    <li class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Item\"><a href=\"../partner/\" class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Link\">\n      <h2 class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Title\">取扱施設検索</h2>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Text\">全国の取扱施設を掲載しています。</p>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Btn\"><span class=\"sw-Btn03\">詳細はこちら</span></p>\n      </a></li>\n    <li class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Item\"><a href=\"qc.html\" class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Link\">\n      <h2 class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Title\">国際基準に基づく品質管理</h2>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Text\">厳しい品質管理に基づき、安全・安心な製品をお届けしています。</p>\n      <p class=\"contactlensfr-Info_Btn\"><span class=\"sw-Btn03\">詳細はこちら</span></p>\n      </a></li>\n  </ul>\n</article>\n<footer class=\"st-Footer\">\n  <section class=\"st-Footer_About\">\n    <h2 class=\"st-Footer_Logo\"><a href=\"../\" class=\"st-Footer_Logo_Link\"><img src=\"../common/img/img_logo_01.svg\" width=\"165\" height=\"35\" alt=\"made in kyoto サンコンタクトレンズ\" class=\"st-Footer_Logo_Image\"></a></h2>\n    <div class=\"st-Footer_NavIcons\">\n      <ul class=\"st-Footer_Nav\">\n        <li class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Item st-Footer_Nav_Item-contactlens\"><a href=\"../contactlens/\" class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Link\">コンタクトレンズ</a></li>\n        <li class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Item st-Footer_Nav_Item-care\"><a href=\"../care/\" class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Link\">ケア用品・通販</a></li>\n        <li class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Item st-Footer_Nav_Item-partner\"><a href=\"../partner/\" class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Link\">取扱施設</a></li>\n        <li class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Item st-Footer_Nav_Item-howtouse\"><a href=\"../howtouse/\" class=\"st-Footer_Nav_Link\">レンズの取扱い方法</a></li>\n        <li clas